{"word":"δυστυχής","slug":"δυστυχής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δυστυχής</b></el> <el>(δυς-τῠχής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τύχη'><el>τύχη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>unlucky, unfortunate</i>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τὰ δυστυχῆ  δυστυχίαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-χῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>ill-starred, harbinger of ill</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}